  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Provides a heart disease presumption for members employed as a fire alarm dispatcher, a supervising fire alarm dispatcher level one or a supervising fire alarm dispatcher level two of a fire department in a city with a population of one million or more."
    }
